---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

const posts = await getCollection('blog');
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="tr">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style is:global>
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=UnifrakturMaguntia&display=swap');

			body {
				background-image: url('/arkaplan5.jpg') !important;
				background-size: cover;
				background-position: center;
				background-attachment: fixed;
			}

			/* ── HEADER LİNKLER ── */
			header nav {
				flex-wrap: wrap; /* Linkler taşarsa alt satıra geçsin */
			}

			header a {
				font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif !important;
				font-weight: 700 !important;
				font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1.1rem) !important; /* Fluid font */
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
				color: #1a1a1a !important;
				background: #e9dcc9 !important;
				padding: 6px 12px !important; /* Mobilde daha küçük padding */
				margin: 4px 3px !important;   /* Sarıldığında boşluk kalsın */
				text-decoration: none !important;
				display: inline-block !important;
				border: 1px solid #3e2723;
				box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px #d4af37;
				transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
				transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
			}

			header a:hover {
				background: #d4af37 !important;
				color: #1a1a1a !important;
				transform: rotate(2deg) translateY(-5px);
				box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px #1a1a1a;
			}

			header a.active {
				border: 2px dashed #1a1a1a;
				background: #d4af37 !important;
			}

			/* ── MAIN KAPSAYICI ── */
			main {
				width: 90%;           /* Sabit 1000px kaldırıldı */
				max-width: 1000px;    /* Masaüstünde hâlâ max 1000px */
				margin: 80px auto 60px;
				background: #fdfaf1;
				padding: clamp(20px, 5vw, 60px); /* Fluid padding */
				border-radius: 5px;
				box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
				border: 1px solid #d4af37;
				color: #2c2c2c;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			/* ── GİRİŞ BÖLÜMÜ ── */
			.intro-wrapper {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 40px;
				justify-content: center;
				flex-wrap: wrap; /* Dar ekranda alt alta geçsin */
			}

			.intro-image {
				flex: 1 1 280px;  /* Büzülüp büyüyebilir, min 280px */
				max-width: 450px;
			}

			.intro-image img {
				width: 100%;       /* Sabit 450px kaldırıldı */
				height: auto;
				border-radius: 20px 0 20px 0;
				filter: sepia(0.2) contrast(1.1);
				box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
				display: block;
			}

			.intro-text {
				flex: 1 1 280px; /* Resimle yan yana, daraldığında alt alta */
			}

			.intro-text h1 {
				font-family: 'UnifrakturMaguntia', cursive !important;
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem); /* Fluid: mobilde küçülür */
				background: #1a1a1a !important;
				color: #fdfaf1 !important;
				padding: 8px 16px !important;
				display: inline-block !important;
				transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
				box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px #d4af37;
				line-height: 1.1;
			}

			.intro-text p {
				background: rgba(253, 250, 241, 0.9);
				padding: 16px;
				border-left: 5px solid #1a1a1a;
				font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem); /* Fluid font */
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #2c2c2c;
				margin-top: 20px;
				box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
			}

			/* ── EDITOR'S PEEK ── */
			.editors-peek {
				margin-top: 60px;
				padding-top: 40px;
				border-top: 3px dashed #1a331a;
			}

			.peek-title {
				font-family: 'UnifrakturMaguntia', cursive !important;
				font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem); /* Fluid font */
				text-align: center;
				color: #1a331a;
				margin-bottom: 40px;
			}

			.peek-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); /* 250→200 */
				gap: 30px;
			}

			.peek-card {
				background: #fdfaf1;
				padding: 25px;
				border: 1px solid #d4af37;
				text-decoration: none;
				color: #2c2c2c;
				position: relative;
				transform: rotate(-1deg);
				box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				box-sizing: border-box; /* Padding taşmasını önler */
			}

			.peek-card:nth-child(even) {
				transform: rotate(1.5deg);
			}

			.peek-card:hover {
				transform: scale(1.05) rotate(0deg);
				box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px #1a331a;
				background: #fff;
			}

			.pin {
				position: absolute;
				top: -10px;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}

			.peek-card h3 {
				font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
				font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem); /* Fluid font */
				margin: 10px 0;
				line-height: 1.2;
				border-bottom: 2px solid #1a331a;
			}

			.peek-card p {
				font-size: 1rem;
				font-style: italic;
				opacity: 0.8;
			}

			/* ── MOBİL BREAKPOINT (≤600px) ── */
			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				main {
					margin: 60px auto 40px;
				}

				.intro-wrapper {
					flex-direction: column; /* Kesinlikle alt alta */
					gap: 24px;
				}

				.intro-image {
					max-width: 100%;
				}

				.peek-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Tek sütun */
					gap: 20px;
				}

				.peek-card {
					transform: rotate(0deg) !important; /* Mobilde yamukluk kaldırıldı */
				}

				header a {
					font-size: 0.7rem !important;
					padding: 5px 8px !important;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="intro-wrapper">
				<div class="intro-image">
					<img src="/illustration1.jpg" alt="Aysun İllüstrasyon" />
				</div>
				<div class="intro-text">
					<h1>Manifesto</h1>
					<p>
						This journal is not only a place where our intellectual and aesthetic works created until now come together; it seeks to go beyond the dominant and single narratives. It is not being done in the usual way that separates ecology, feminism, cinema, literature, and political thought; it exposes the interplay among these areas.
We are not pretending to be impartial. This journal is writing from a leftist viewpoint, opposing the acceptance of capital, patriarchy, and power relations as normal. It denounces the commercialization of nature, control over people, and the disposal of history.
To us, cinema is not just another art form; it is a atmosphere that clearly reveals how power, desire, and ideology are intertwined. On the other hand, literature is being seen as the voice of the oppressed, the unmentionable, and the weak. Ecology and feminism are not the minor topics of this periodical; they are at the seed  our understanding of the world.
This publication does not want to be a platform for oppressive views. Rather, it seeks the plural, split into different phase, and difficult inquiries. Beginning with the urban space, the human body, the environment, and the past, it aspires to uncover the silenced voices.
What is presented here is not for fast consumption but for a pause, a thought and a resistance.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="editors-peek">
				<h2 class="peek-title">Editor's Peek</h2>
				<div class="peek-grid">
					{posts.slice(0, 3).map((post) => (
						<a href={`/blog/${post.slug}/`} class="peek-card">
							<span class="pin">📌</span>
							<h3>{post.data.title}</h3>
							<p>{post.data.description.substring(0, 60)}...</p>
						</a>
					))}
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>